article_title: Candidate for U.S. Senate visits Clark County 4-H Fair
article_text:
Jeffersonville, IN (47130)

Today

Scattered thunderstorms in the morning, then partly cloudy late. High 87F. Winds SSW at 10 to 20 mph. Chance of rain 40%..

Tonight

Scattered thunderstorms in the evening. Partly cloudy skies overnight. Low 67F. Winds S at 5 to 10 mph. Chance of rain 40%.

article_metadata.author: BY ELIZABETH DEPOMPEI

og.description: Editor's note: This is a corrected version of the original story. The figure for the $800 million deficit was incorrect in the original story.
